#

Kefir Berry Smoothie Bowl

10 min
$5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

DairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Sugar

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastHealthySmoothie Bowl

Description

A refreshing and nutritious kefir smoothie bowl topped with fresh berries and a hint of honey. Perfect for a quick breakfast or snack!

Ingredients

  • kefir: 1 cup
  • frozen mixed berries: 1 cup
  • banana: 1 medium
  • chia seeds: 2 tablespoons
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
  • granola: 1/4 cup
  • fresh mint leaves: for garnish
